NVIDIA DRIVER LICENSE NOTICE:

This project contains scripts and patches for installing the NVIDIA proprietary
driver. The NVIDIA driver itself is subject to NVIDIA's End User License Agreement:
https://www.nvidia.com/en-us/drivers/nvidia-license/

The patches included are derived from community sources (RPM Fusion, ALT Linux)
and are distributed under their respective licenses (GPL-compatible).

This project does NOT include the NVIDIA driver binary. Users must download it
separately from NVIDIA's official website.

